      "description": "This E46 M3 is a mechanically sound example of BMW\u2019s high-revving S54 inline-six, delivering power through six individual throttle bodies and dual-VANOS variable valve timing. The 6-speed manual gearbox offers precise engagement, paired with a variable M differential lock for optimal torque vectoring. It features a well-maintained suspension geometry and inspected subframe mounting points, ensuring the chassis handles high-lateral loads with composure. A true driver\u2019s car with linear power delivery and a visceral 8,000 RPM redline, this vehicle is sorted for the spirited purist.",
